caption: We arrived at this place for a meeting. my friend recommended this place.  Well, we were not disappointed. The crew welcomed us with a smile and we felt fantastic. The food was just great. We loved this spot a lot and we will visit this place again. Recommended.
I eat in this spot a lot since I work right next to it. I have to say the service is always great and they keep the place clean all the time. Rates are reasonable and they serve big portions.
